{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"99794-shen-chu-ni-de-shetou","title":"伸出你的舌头！","description":"你认为所有的舌头都像你的一样柔软和粉红色吗？ 动物有各种形状，大小和颜色的舌头。 他们以不同的方式使用他们的舌头，但不像人类那样，使用舌头来说话。","language":"Chinese (Simplified)","langCode":"zh","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jala Community"],"illustrators":["Sandhya Prabhat"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/99794-shen-chu-ni-de-shetou"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/724139/size3/a690782932e9a84bf87b3e0184a17cfc.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/724139/size6/a690782932e9a84bf87b3e0184a17cfc.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54981/size6/515c01c0a5a2abd59f4917b0cfa02600.jpg","text":"蓝舌头\n黑舌头","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54982/size6/a430ef3857608fae80397fdaa907510d.jpg","text":"长舌头\n强舌头","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54983/size6/af6b103d3a35c62c002c34b83d31f855.jpg","text":"尖尖的舌头\n粘粘的舌头","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54984/size6/9a698accf2f15604b1767e805b0b7588.jpg","text":"粗粗的舌头\n滑滑的舌头","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54985/size6/8413654bfc8e71d8a99f3fdfe46b1d16.jpg","text":"分叉的舌头\n快速的舌头","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54986/size6/c0df5d6a56c1321298c49d5a94dfb19d.jpg","text":"沉重的舌头\n毛毛的舌头","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/54987/size6/a50ef95df00b7f27c7d32778e8ce28a3.jpg","text":"你的舌头是什么样子呢？","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55095/size6/8e2dd636d681ea17f2a9a611ac763860.jpg","text":"我们来谈谈舌头\n你知道舌头是由肌肉制成的，并能够做很多不同的事吗？ 然而，舌头永远不会感到疲倦或疼痛！\n北极熊的蓝舌头吸收太阳的热量来保暖。\n长颈鹿的舌头是暗色的，可以保护它免受非洲大草原的晒伤。\n穿山甲把它长长的舌头放入蚁丘，以啜饮蚂蚁 - 它最喜欢的零食。","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55062/size6/5e667bd31c64b4e747b93fecc93a7d5b.jpg","text":"蝾螈射出强大的舌头来抢夺蟋蟀和果蝇。\n鹅用尖尖的舌头抓住草，把它撕下来来吃。\n青蛙用它粘粘的唾液和有弹性的舌头捕捉苍蝇。","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55063/size6/1a39f8e4c00c2a461ac406c960b546a7.jpg","text":"猫的粗粗的舌头帮助它刷毛皮。\n当狗太热时，狗把会肿起来的舌头伸出来。\n蛇用它分叉的舌头闻周围的气味。","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/55064/size6/5a6125c753a3b0c30e27f4dd37447dcd.jpg","text":"变色龙的舌头以闪电般的速度飞出来抓住蚱蜢，然后才跳起来。\n蓝鲸是地球上最大的动物，拥有最重的舌头，有助于捕获它喜欢吃的微小磷虾。\n火烈鸟的毛毛舌头有助于过滤蓝绿藻和虾，它最喜欢的食物。","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":30}}